name: Triple H (long hair) - Textual Inversion
description:
This is a textual inversion trained on pictures of wrestler Triple H, aka Paul Michael Levesque, with his old school long hair. You can find his newer look here.

I am amazed on how good the images came out in my test runs, hopefully you have as much fun as I have.

Please let me know and showcase some images.

Still learning and improving the progress of the training, any feedback is welcome.

Feel free to leave me a tip/buy me a coffee if you like what I am doing :)
